title: Two Sides to Every Date: I NEVER Get Ghosted
description: Josh is calling in to find out what happened with Danielle.  They recently had their first date and he thought it went super well but now she's ghosted him and he claims that he NEVER gets ghosted.   We talk to Danielle to find out what happened.
